default4) How effectively do Community Transport services address the needs of p
defaultassengers in isolated communities? How could Community Transport be improved?
default&#xa0;
defaultA
default lot of good work has been done in this area but lack of long term core funding, and of coordinated integration and marketing strategies has not helped in fulfilling the full p
defaultotential of
default this mode. Three year funding, for example, is too short to allow investment in capital projects which may take longer to achieve payback. This argument has also been a criticism of short duration Rail franchises. 
default&#xa0;
defaultThere needs to be funding fo
defaultr at least seven years, or ten to allow more imaginative solutions to be tried with the chance of being able to become revenue neutral over the full period.
